headline: Prediction: 2 Stocks That Will Be Worth More Than United States Steel 5 Years From Now
summary: United States Steel is an iconic steelmaker, but it is no longer an industry leader.  Nucor and Steel Dynamics are both built on more modern steelmaking technology.  Nucor and Steel Dynamics both have stronger growth models then US Steel.

headline: 1 Magnificent Dividend Stock Down 33% to Buy and Hold Forever
summary: Nucor is a leading steel stock in the U.S. with a history spanning over 100 years.  Given the sector's cyclical nature, investors should prepare to ride out its ups and downs.  While President Donald Trump's announcement of tariffs sent markets into a temporary tailspin, many stocks have since recovered.
